7. **[^](#cite_ref-199)** That is, among respondents who have done "extensive development work [with Rust] in over the past year" (14.8%), Rust had the largest percentage who also expressed interest to "work in [Rust] over the next year" (72.4%). [&#91; 191 &#93;](#cite_note-SO-2025-survey-197)

